---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const frontmatter = {
  title: 'O RespireLabs',
  description: 'Nasza misja, zasady i dlaczego tworzymy trenera oddychania z priorytetem prywatnosci.',
  lang: 'pl',
  alternatePaths: {
    en: '/en/about',
    de: '/de/ueber-uns',
    pl: '/pl/o-nas'
  }
};
---

<Layout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative bg-brand-white min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-24 pb-20 border-b border-brand-light/60">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none blur-[100px] mix-blend-multiply">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-blue rounded-full animate-[pulse_10s_ease-in-out_infinite]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal hero-reveal flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 glass-panel px-5 py-2 rounded-full mb-8 shadow-sm">
        <span class="text-xs font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-dark/80">O nas</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-tighter mb-6 leading-[0.9] drop-shadow-sm">
        Tworzymy <br/>
        <span class="text-gradient">trenera oddychania.</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#F5F5F7]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-montserrat font-bold text-brand-blue uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Nasza misja</h2>
      <p class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-garamond italic text-brand-dark/90 leading-tight">
        "Chcemy, aby zdrowsze nawyki oddechowe byly dostepne, mierzalne i respektujace prywatnosc â€” tak, aby wiecej osob budzilo sie z lepszym snem i wieksza energia."
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE ARE BUILDING -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-brand-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Co tworzymy.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-10 shadow-sm border border-black/[0.03] reveal-left">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-brand-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                  <img src="/assets/icons/respire-labs-icons_microphone.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="w-8 h-8 opacity-70" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Aplikacja</h3>
              <p class="text-lg font-montserrat font-light text-brand-grey">Trener oddychania na telefon, wykrywajacy wzorce i dostarczajacy powiadomienia w czasie rzeczywistym bez dodatkowego sprzetu.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-10 shadow-sm border border-black/[0.03] reveal delay-100">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-brand-yellow/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                  <img src="/assets/icons/respire-labs-icons_tape.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="w-8 h-8 opacity-70" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Smart Mouth Tape</h3>
              <p class="text-lg font-montserrat font-light text-brand-grey">Opcjonalna koncepcja urzadzenia noszonego do precyzyjnych, klinicznych danych o oddychaniu podczas snu.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-10 shadow-sm border border-black/[0.03] reveal-right">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#F5F5F7] flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
                  <span class="text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">ðŸŒ±</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Platforma wellness</h3>
              <p class="text-lg font-montserrat font-light text-brand-grey">Dlugoterminowa platforma wellness oddechowego oferujaca edukacje, sledzenie trendow i coaching nawykow.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRINCIPLES -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-brand-dark text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern-dark opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold mb-4">Nasze zasady.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="glass-panel-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 reveal-left">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-3">Prywatnosc przede wszystkim</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat font-light text-brand-light/70">Lokalne przetwarzanie i wyrazna zgoda. Twoje nagrania oddechowe nigdy nie opuszczaja urzadzenia, chyba ze sam to zdecydujesz.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-panel-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 reveal-right">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-3">Odpowiedzialne twierdzenia</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat font-light text-brand-light/70">Tworzymy narzedzia wellness, a nie diagnostyczne urzadzenia medyczne. Jestesmy uczciwi co do mozliwosci naszych produktow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-panel-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 reveal-left delay-100">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-3">Zmiana nawykow zamiast szumu</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat font-light text-brand-light/70">Nie sprzedajemy tylko sprzetu. Dostarczamy petle coachingowe niezbedne do faktycznej zmiany nawykow oddechowych.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-panel-dark rounded-[2rem] p-10 reveal-right delay-100">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-yellow mb-3">Jasne, uzyteczne informacje</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat font-light text-brand-light/70">Przeksztalcamy zlozozone dane oddechowe w proste "najlepsze kolejne kroki", ktore kazdy moze zrozumiec, dzieki zaawansowanej sztucznej inteligencji i uczeniu maszynowemu.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EARLY MOMENTUM -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#F7F7F9] border-y border-brand-light/40">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20 reveal">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full mb-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-montserrat font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-blue">Kamienie milowe</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-dark mb-6">Wczesna dynamika.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Dopiero zaczynamy, ale postep jest realny.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center reveal delay-100">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">2K+</div>
          <p class="text-sm font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Zapisow na liste oczekujacych</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center reveal delay-200">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">3</div>
          <p class="text-sm font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Otrzymane granty i nagrody</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center reveal delay-300">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">2025</div>
          <p class="text-sm font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Zalozona w Tyrolu, Austria</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center reveal delay-400">
          <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Q2</div>
          <p class="text-sm font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Cel uruchomienia bety aplikacji</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOURNEY TIMELINE -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-brand-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">Nasza droga.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-brand-light" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <!-- Timeline items -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 reveal">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-12">
              <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-brand-blue text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">2024</div>
              <h3 class="font-oddval text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Pomysl sie rodzi</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Po latach zmagania sie z oddychaniem przez usta i braku rozwiazania laczacego sledzenie z coachingiem, narodzila sie koncepcja RespireLabs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-blue border-4 border-brand-white" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 reveal delay-100">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-12"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow border-4 border-brand-white" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
              <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-brand-blue text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Poczatek 2025</div>
              <h3 class="font-oddval text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Granty i uznanie</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Otrzymano finansowanie aws First Incubator, wsparcie WKO Tirol i nominacje do Tiroler Innovationspreis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 reveal delay-200">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-12">
              <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-brand-blue text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Polowa 2025</div>
              <h3 class="font-oddval text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Rozpoczecie rozwoju aplikacji</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Opracowano glowne algorytmy wykrywania oddychania. Zaprojektowano architekture privacy-first. Zaproszono pierwszych beta testerow.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-blue border-4 border-brand-white" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 reveal delay-300">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-12"></div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow border-4 border-brand-white" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
              <div class="font-montserrat font-bold text-brand-blue text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Teraz</div>
              <h3 class="font-oddval text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">W drodze do uruchomienia</h3>
              <p class="font-montserrat text-brand-grey font-light">Beta aplikacji tuz za rogiem. Prototypowanie Smart Mouth Tape w toku. Rosnaca spolecznosc 2000+ czlonkow listy oczekujacych.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEAM -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-[#F5F5F7]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-12">Zespol</h2>
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[var(--surface-card)] rounded-[2rem] p-12 shadow-sm border border-brand-light dark:border-white/10">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-brand-light/50 dark:bg-white/10 mx-auto flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ‘‹</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-oddval font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Krzysztof Dabrowski</h3>
            <p class="font-montserrat font-medium text-brand-blue uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-6">Zalozyciel / Wizja / Tlen</p>
            <p class="font-garamond text-xl text-brand-grey max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Pasjonat health-tech i wellness oddechowego. Buduje przyszlosc komfortu snu z Tyrolu w Austrii.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-8">
                <a href="mailto:kdabrowski@respirelabs.com" class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-brand-dark hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">kdabrowski@respirelabs.com</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOIN THE MOVEMENT -->
  <section class="bg-brand-dark py-32 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern-dark opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[600px] bg-brand-blue/20 blur-[150px] pointer-events-none mix-blend-screen"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-oddval font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-8">Dolacz do ruchu.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-montserrat font-light text-brand-light/70 mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Tworzymy cos znaczacego. Dolacz do 2000+ osob, ktore wierza, ze lepsze oddychanie prowadzi do lepszego zycia.
      </p>
      <a href="/pl/lista-oczekujacych" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 py-5 bg-brand-blue text-white font-montserrat text-lg font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-blue-600 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-[0_8px_20px_rgba(32,111,247,0.3)] transition-all duration-300 focus-ring-dark">Dolacz do listy oczekujacych</a>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-garamond text-brand-light/40 italic">To nie jest urzadzenie medyczne. Nie diagnozuje ani nie leczy schorzen.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>